body:
Hello everyone,

My name is Joe, i'm 18 years old and I'm looking for a progressive Team to grind FlexQ up to Master-Tier+.

I'm currently P5 in SoloQ & i'm experienced playing in a Team.
I'm always looking to improve and i'm not sensitive to criticism. 

Hit me up on Discord so we can talk about an application.

Discord: Ravensince#5055
